    87Ôćĺ### ky(input, options?)
    88Ôćĺ
    89ÔćĺThe `input` and `options` are the same as [`fetch`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope/fetch), with additional `options` available (see below).
